test_odd_same_number:
assert [-11, -11, -11, -11] == [-11, -11]
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: -11
  Full diff:
  - [-11, -11]
  + [-11, -11, -11, -11]
test_all_one_range:
assert [1, 1, 1, 1] == [1, 1]
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 1
  Full diff:
  - [1, 1]
  + [1, 1, 1, 1]
